query: UPDATE sites SET mapMarkerX = NULL, mapMarkerY = NULL WHERE id IN (SELECT id FROM sites WHERE centreId = (SELECT id FROM shopping_centres WHERE name = 'Highlands Marketplace') AND (siteNumber LIKE '%Site 3%' OR siteNumber LIKE '%Site 5%'));
